[
  {
    "id": 0,
    "text": "、多分このイラストが最初に出たのか?",
    "start_time": 3179.84,
    "end_time": 3183.64,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 1,
    "text": "みんなちょっと、、見切れた有咲ちゃんが、ちょっと映ってた",
    "start_time": 3184.92,
    "end_time": 3188.92,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "text": "画像とか、Twitterとかに上がってたけど。",
    "start_time": 3190.64,
    "end_time": 3193.32,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 3,
    "text": "本当さ、誰だこの女はみたいな、",
    "start_time": 3194.24,
    "end_time": 3198.12,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 4,
    "text": "、なるよ。",
    "start_time": 3199.04,
    "end_time": 3199.96,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 5,
    "text": "本当このイラストもさなん、この1枚絵だけ見、すごくこう雫は朗らかな表情をしている、",
    "start_time": 3200.56,
    "end_time": 3209.16,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 6,
    "text": "かと思ったら愛莉ちゃんが、シャーってしてる、、有咲ちゃんはふんって感じだ、",
    "start_time": 3209.16,
    "end_time": 3213.9,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 7,
    "text": "なんか本当面白いんだ、ストーリー見た後だとねなるほどなって感じだよ。",
    "start_time": 3213.9,
    "end_time": 3219.12,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 8,
    "text": "。",
    "start_time": 3219.96,
    "end_time": 3220.64,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 9,
    "text": "、本当に好きな、この、有咲ちゃんもたまらん、愛莉ちゃんのこの表情も、",
    "start_time": 3221.48,
    "end_time": 3228.1,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 10,
    "text": "すごく。",
    "start_time": 3228.1,
    "end_time": 3228.96,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 11,
    "text": "、お次が穂乃果ちゃん。",
    "start_time": 3229.8,
    "end_time": 3231.28,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 12,
    "text": "めっちゃ可愛く?",
    "start_time": 3232.48,
    "end_time": 3233.6,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 13,
    "text": "特訓。",
    "start_time": 3233.6,
    "end_time": 3234.72,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 14,
    "text": "すっごい。",
    "start_time": 3236.24,
    "end_time": 3238.06,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 15,
    "text": "、、雫が着てた衣装とまた打って変わっ、白黒で赤がアクセントに入ってたりとかしてめっちゃ可愛いよ。",
    "start_time": 3238.06,
    "end_time": 3247.6,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 16,
    "text": "この葉っぱ、",
    "start_time": 3248.84,
    "end_time": 3249.68,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 17,
    "text": "葉っぱを、頭にかぶってるところとかさすっごい可愛く?",
    "start_time": 3250.4,
    "end_time": 3255.4,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 18,
    "text": "コロポックルって私さっき",
    "start_time": 3256.16,
    "end_time": 3257.6,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 19,
    "text": "、、言っちゃったんだけど、、なんか妖精感があってめっちゃ。",
    "start_time": 3259.64,
    "end_time": 3263.76,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 20,
    "text": "、こちらが特訓。",
    "start_time": 3264.96,
    "end_time": 3268.72,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 21,
    "text": "もぐもぐタイム。",
    "start_time": 3268.72,
    "end_time": 3270.0,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 22,
    "text": "、マジ、あのプロセカの現場でもそうなんだ、控え室にね美味しいものをいつも用意していただくん、",
    "start_time": 3270.0,
    "end_time": 3280.64,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 23,
    "text": "皆、本当。",
    "start_time": 3280.64,
    "end_time": 3282.12,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 24,
    "text": "今日も、お弁当いただいたんだ、こうやって、お菓子とか置いてある。",
    "start_time": 3282.8,
    "end_time": 3287.12,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 25,
    "text": "結構リアルだ。",
    "start_time": 3287.12,
    "end_time": 3288.28,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 26,
    "text": "この、なんか本番前に、緊張で相まっ、でもお菓子美味しいから食べ、",
    "start_time": 3290.16,
    "end_time": 3295.36,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 27,
    "text": "もぐもぐみたい。",
    "start_time": 3295.36,
    "end_time": 3296.6,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 28,
    "text": "このサイドストーリーも是非見て欲しい。",
    "start_time": 3296.6,
    "end_time": 3299.38,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 29,
    "text": "本当。",
    "start_time": 3299.38,
    "end_time": 3300.04,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  }
]